OL,6,FThe leader of Rhondda Cynon Taf
OL,7,FCouncil, whose area was severely
OL,8,Faffected by Storm Bert flooding, has
OL,9,Fcalled for a full review of the
OL,10,Fwarning system operated by Natural
OL,11,FResources Wales.
OL,13,FNRW has come under criticism after the
OL,14,Fflooding, with some residents in
OL,15,FPontypridd - which suffered severe
OL,16,Fflooding in 2020 after Storm Dennis -
OL,17,Fsaying warnings only came after the
OL,18,FRiver Taff broke its banks.
