OL,3,CCalls for full review of system used
OL,4,Cto warn people of flooding threat
OL,6,FA total of 433 properties were
OL,7,Fimpacted across Wales, as well as
OL,8,Finfrastructure, after the substantial
OL,9,Fwind and rain brought by Storm Bert.
OL,10,FBetween 200 and 300 properties were
OL,11,Faffected in Rhondda Cynon Taf alone.
OL,13,FCouncillor Andrew Morgan said data
OL,14,Ffrom water level monitoring stations
OL,15,Fshows that warnings did not come early
OL,16,Fenough on Sunday, 24 November, and
OL,17,Fthat "something is fundamentally
OL,18,Fwrong" with the warning sending system.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/27
