OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F464A1732746387
OL,3,CCalls for full review of system used
OL,4,Cto warn people of flooding threat
OL,6,F"The suggestion is that the system
OL,7,Fworked from their side, they say that
OL,8,Fthe trigger points that are set for
OL,9,Fthe warnings to be issued were met,
OL,10,Fbut that means that there is a
OL,11,Ffundamental issue with the trigger
OL,12,Fpoints for the warning system," he
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"If they just looked at own gauges
OL,16,Fthey should have seen at 6.30am on
OL,17,FSunday something seriously going wrong.
OL,19,F"Something has fundamentally gone
OL,20,Fwrong with the warning system here in
OL,21,FPontypridd."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/27
