OL,3,CCalls for full review of system used
OL,4,Cto warn people of flooding threat
OL,6,FNRW has committed to reviewing the
OL,7,Fwarnings issued to residents about the
OL,8,Fseverity of Storm Bert, while Cllr
OL,9,FMorgan is calling for a "joined-up
OL,10,Freview" by all the agencies involved.
OL,12,F"What we need to make sure of is the
OL,13,Foutcome in terms of the preparedness,
OL,14,Fthe response on the time, which seems
OL,15,Fto be reasonable in terms of the
OL,16,Fresponse, but actually it's the
OL,17,Fwarning system I have the concerns
OL,18,Fwith," he said.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/27
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
