OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F464A1732746387
OL,3,CCalls for full review of system used
OL,4,Cto warn people of flooding threat
OL,6,F"And I have to say, I think when I met
OL,7,Fwith the NRW (on Tuesday), they
OL,8,Fconceded, and they did acknowledge
OL,9,Fthat there needs to be a review, and
OL,10,Fmaybe the trigger points that they do
OL,11,Fuse are not correct.
OL,13,F"My view is, as things currently
OL,14,Fstand, if we had another storm next
OL,15,Fweek, if the Met Office issues a
OL,16,Fyellow warning and the flood guidance
OL,17,Fstatement isn't updated, and NRW uses
OL,18,Fthe same process, then this could
OL,19,Fhappen again.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/27
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
