OL,3,CCalls for full review of system used
OL,4,Cto warn people of flooding threat
OL,6,F"Everybody has to be held to account
OL,7,Fin terms of the organisations.
OL,9,F"The staff I've been dealing with in
OL,10,FNRW, I think, have been very open and
OL,11,Fvery frank about some of the
OL,12,Fconversations we've had over the last
OL,13,F24 hours in terms of leadership of the
OL,14,Forganisation. I think that's for
OL,15,Fothers to decide."
OL,17,FIt comes after First Minister of Wales
OL,18,FEluned Morgan insisted flood defences
OL,19,Fprotected thousands of homes after
OL,20,FStorm Bert battered the country.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/27
