OL,6,FEluned Morgan said fewer homes were
OL,7,Fflooded at the weekend than in
OL,8,Fprevious years, insisting a
OL,9,F"significant number" of people were
OL,10,Fprotected. However, she said better
OL,11,Fflood warnings will be needed in the
OL,12,Ffuture.
