OL,6,FBaroness Morgan said: "NRW issued 131
OL,7,Falerts and warnings, including two
OL,8,Fsevere flood warnings, with over
OL,9,F95,000 messages sent and 46,000-plus
OL,10,Fcustomers being reached. So they did
OL,11,Fquite a lot. The question is, could
OL,12,Fthey have done more? And that is
OL,13,Fsomething, clearly, that will need to
OL,14,Fbe analysed."
OL,16,FWhat has Natural Resources Wales said?
