OL,6,FDavid Letellier, head of South Wales
OL,7,FCentral operations at Natural
OL,8,FResources Wales, said: "In the lead-up
OL,9,Fto any significant rainfall event, we
OL,10,Fwork with our colleagues at the Met
OL,11,FOffice and the Flood Forecasting
OL,12,FCentre (FFC), and use the modelling
OL,13,Fand forecasts available to us to
OL,14,Fensure our teams are prepared and
OL,15,Fready to respond.
