OL,3,CCalls for full review of system used
OL,4,Cto warn people of flooding threat
OL,6,F"Our rainfall and river gauge network
OL,7,Fare also constantly in operation.
OL,8,FGiven the uncertainty around the
OL,9,Fpotential impacts of this event, we
OL,10,Ftook steps from Wednesday last week to
OL,11,Fmake sure our response team rotas were
OL,12,Fwell staffed and prepared to tackle
OL,13,Fwhatever the storm would bring.
OL,15,F"Our message to professional partners
OL,16,Fand the public from Wednesday last
OL,17,Fweek ahead of Storm Bert was that
OL,18,Fsignificant flooding was possible
OL,19,Facross Wales and to be prepared."
