OL,6,F"On the Friday before the storm, we
OL,7,Fissued a widely used press release
OL,8,Fwarning of potential widespread
OL,9,Fflooding," he said. "Throughout the
OL,10,Fevent, we provided regular updates on
OL,11,Fthe most serious flood warnings via
OL,12,Fsocial media channels, which were
OL,13,Fwidely shared by partner
OL,14,Forganisations, public figures such as
OL,15,Fpoliticians, and concerned members of
OL,16,Fthe public. To ensure clear
OL,17,Fcommunication of the risks and
OL,18,Fimpacts, we established a robust
OL,19,Fspokesperson rota, enabling us to
OL,20,Fconduct over 25 interviews with major
OL,21,Flocal and national media outlets
OL,22,Facross radio and television.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/27
