OL,6,F"NRW worked with our multi-agency
OL,7,Fpartners including the Wales Warning
OL,8,Fand Informing Group to highlight the
OL,9,Fneed for proactive communications
OL,10,Fabout the forthcoming storm. We used
OL,11,Fsocial media to highlight the
OL,12,Fpotential for signficant flooding
OL,13,Fimpacts to the Wales Community Flood
OL,14,FVolunteer network via Facebook.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G13/27
