OL,6,F"This was a significant event and the
OL,7,Fnaming of the storm by the Met Office
OL,8,Freflected its potential impacts -
OL,9,Fincluding flooding. The impacts were
OL,10,Fpredicted to be significant but with
OL,11,Funcertainty about precise location of
OL,12,Fimpact.
OL,14,F"Over the course of the storm, we
OL,15,Fissued two Severe flood warnings, 66
OL,16,Fflood warnings and 65 flood alerts
OL,17,Facross Wales which went to over 46,000
OL,18,Fproperties.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G14/27
