OL,4,Cto warn people of flooding threat
OL,6,F"While all parts of Wales felt the
OL,7,Fimpacts, the amount of rainfall that
OL,8,Ffell across south Wales was
OL,9,Fparticularly significant. We issued a
OL,10,Fflood alert for the River Taff at
OL,11,FPontypridd on Saturday giving people
OL,12,Fadvance warning that flooding was
OL,13,Fpossible, and to be prepared.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G15/27
