OL,6,F"Early on Sunday morning, a very
OL,7,Fintense, localised area of rain fell
OL,8,Fin the Taff catchment, with up to
OL,9,F160mm recorded at some locations. A
OL,10,Fflood warning was issued ` which
OL,11,Fadvises that flooding is expected, and
OL,12,Fimmediate action is required - for the
OL,13,FRiver Taff at Pontypridd at 7:41am on
OL,14,FSunday when the river reached the
OL,15,Fflood warning trigger level.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G16/27
