OL,6,F"There were also two severe flood
OL,7,Fwarnings issued - which means there is
OL,8,Fa danger to life - for the River
OL,9,FMonnow at Skenfrith - issued at 3.05pm
OL,10,Fon Sunday and the River Monnow at
OL,11,FForge Road, Osbaston - issued at
OL,12,F3.06pm on Sunday.
