OL,6,F"These stood up to the test of Storm
OL,7,FBert, but we cannot change the rate at
OL,8,Fwhich some of our rivers will rise
OL,9,Fwhen there is locally intense and
OL,10,Ftorrential rainfall," he said. "As we
OL,11,Fdo after every serious flood incident,
OL,12,Fwe are carrying out our own proactive
OL,13,Frecovery and review work to ensure
OL,14,Fthat we can learn any lessons from the
OL,15,Fexperience and use those learnings to
OL,16,Fmake any further improvements
OL,17,Fnecessary."
