OL,6,FIt comes after Baroness Morgan used
OL,7,FFirst Minister's Questions on Tuesday
OL,8,Fto announce new financial support for
OL,9,Fthose whose homes were flooded over
OL,10,Fthe weekend.
OL,12,FThe funding will allow affected
OL,13,Fhouseholds to receive grants of #500,
OL,14,For #1000 for those without insurance.
OL,16,FThe First Minister also faced calls
OL,17,Ffrom Plaid Cymru to demand more
OL,18,Ffunding from Westminster to improve
OL,19,Fcoal tip safety, but she said it would
OL,20,Fbe "difficult" to spend more than the
OL,21,F#25 million given this year.
