OL,6,FShe insisted lessons had been learned
OL,7,Fsince Storm Dennis in 2020, with #300
OL,8,Fmillion having been invested in
OL,9,Fdefences and support.
OL,11,F"I think that it is important to note
OL,12,F` particularly in places like Rhondda
OL,13,FCynon Taff, for example, where last
OL,14,Ftime about 2,000 homes were affected `
